OL,3,CHow ITV News got teams on the ground
OL,4,Cas Iran conflict erupted
OL,6,FFollowing the outbreak of the war in
OL,7,FIran, we have had questions come in
OL,8,Fabout exactly how ITV News has managed
OL,9,Fto get so many teams on the ground to
OL,10,Fcover the story ever since the US and
OL,11,FIsrael started missile strikes on
OL,12,FSaturday.
OL,14,FIt is always a big challenge
OL,15,Flogistically for news teams around the
OL,16,Fworld.
OL,18,FWe have a team in London who are,
OL,19,Fthankfully, well-versed in making sure
OL,20,Fthat flights get booked where they can
OL,21,Fbe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772582588
OL,3,CHow ITV News got teams on the ground
OL,4,Cas Iran conflict erupted
OL,6,FThey also take care of logistics, such
OL,7,Fas booking hotels, organising fixers
OL,8,Fand drivers on the ground, and making
OL,9,Fsure that people can get to their
OL,10,Flocations safely - even in active war
OL,11,Fzones.
OL,13,FHear Julie's first-hand account of
OL,14,Fgetting into the Middle East
OL,16,FI have been reporting from Erbil in
OL,17,Fnorthern Iraq, alongside our
OL,18,FInternational Editor Emma Murphy and
OL,19,Fall of our producers and camera crews.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
