FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772582588
OL,3,CHow ITV News got teams on the ground
OL,4,Cas Iran conflict erupted
OL,6,FWe got in very late on Sunday after a
OL,7,F30-hour trip from Heathrow on Saturday
OL,8,Fmorning.
OL,10,FWe've also got teams in Israel, Dubai,
OL,11,FCyprus, and Lebanon, so it has been
OL,12,Fquite the operation.
OL,14,FBut of course, with very many decades
OL,15,Fof experience, ITV News knows how to
OL,16,Fmove pretty quickly when a big story
OL,17,Flike this breaks.
OL,19,FHow did we get to northern Iraq?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772582588
OL,3,CHow ITV News got teams on the ground
OL,4,Cas Iran conflict erupted
OL,6,FWe set out on Saturday morning with a
OL,7,Fflight from Heathrow to Istanbul,
OL,8,Fthinking we might be able to get to
OL,9,FJordan.
OL,11,FWe got to Istanbul, had a couple of
OL,12,Fhours' sleep, and then got another
OL,13,Fflight out of Istanbul to eastern
OL,14,FTurkey.
OL,16,FOff that flight, we met a series of
OL,17,Fdrivers who'd been arranged for us who
OL,18,Fbrought us all the way down to the
OL,19,Fborder with Iraq, which was about a
OL,20,Ffour-hour drive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772582588
OL,3,CHow ITV News got teams on the ground
OL,4,Cas Iran conflict erupted
OL,6,FThe border crossing itself can take a
OL,7,Fbit of time, because we're travelling
OL,8,Fwith a lot of kit - not only cameras,
OL,9,Fbut all of the engineering stuff that
OL,10,Fwe have with us when we're presenting
OL,11,Ftoo - but thankfully it went pretty
OL,12,Fsmoothly.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772582588
OL,3,CHow ITV News got teams on the ground
OL,4,Cas Iran conflict erupted
OL,6,FWe then had another team of drivers
OL,7,Fmeet us on the Iraq side of the
OL,8,FTurkish border, and then it was about
OL,9,Fanother four-hour drive down to Erbil.
OL,11,FEven as we were driving in, you could
OL,12,Fhear the interceptors going up to stop
OL,13,Fthe missiles, which were being aimed
OL,14,Fat the US base about eight miles away
OL,15,Fnear the airport.
OL,17,FSo it was very clear that we were
OL,18,Farriving just as this war was
OL,19,Fbeginning to spread across the region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772582588
OL,3,CHow ITV News got teams on the ground
OL,4,Cas Iran conflict erupted
OL,6,FThankfully, we got into the hotel safe
OL,7,Fand sound and we managed to get on air
OL,8,Fon Sunday night.
OL,10,FThis is just one picture - all of our
OL,11,Fteams had pretty similar, complex
OL,12,Fjourneys.
OL,14,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,15,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,16,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,17,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
